strings.Value: "I came to purge this place of evil!"
"Vordakai summoned me. I am here at his request."

{n}A figure lies shrouded in darkness in the center of the room — the stench of decay emanates from it in waves, enough to make your breath catch in your throat. As you choke back the urge to vomit, the figure turns to reveal a misshapen skull with blazing eyes.{/n} "Who comes?"
"A servant of death, a keeper of darkness... and all its victims. Now answer my question lest you join them!"
"Hmm… you do not belong here. Leave!"
{n}Kanerah shivers and turns away, hiding a sudden pallor.{/n} "Daemons... I hate those creatures, along with everything else that crawls out of Abaddon!"
